nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 67 is the sixty-seventh issue of Star Wars Insider magazine. It was released to newsstands on April 15, 2003. The subscriber-exclusive edition of issue 67 included the third volume of Bantha Tracks, the Official Star Wars Fan Club newsletter. This issue also came packaged with a special poster to commemorate the twentieth anniversary of the original trilogy film Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi.
